data_graphene_model
# CrystalAR educational 2D model, not a three-dimensional experimental CIF.
# The in-plane hexagonal lattice parameter is based on experimental graphite/graphene values.
# A 4 x 4 in-plane patch is written explicitly for useful browser visualization.
# c = 20 A is an artificial vacuum spacing used only to represent an isolated monolayer.
_chemical_name_common 'Graphene monolayer (educational 2D model)'
